refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
boolcanCompress
This should be used to test whether compression is possible prior to loading a phar archive containing compressed files.

  &reftitle.examples;



    A canCompress example


<?php
if (Phar::canCompress()) {
    echo file_get_contents('phar://whatever.phar/internal/file.txt');
} else {
    echo 'no compression available';
}
?>
